noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "liu2019atomically"
literal "true"

\end_inset

 Because of this is important to establish the stoichiometry and lattice
 stacking of the crystals used in our devices.
 X-Ray diffraction displayed peaks corresponding to the 
\begin_inset Formula $R3m$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $R\bar{3}m$
\end_inset

 space groups.
 Raman showed peaks near 104, 179, and 193 
\begin_inset Formula $cm^{-1}$
\end_inset

corresponding to the 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}^{\,1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $E^{3}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}^{\,4}$
\end_inset

